{"tid":801301,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【廢鐵通車】紅雨淹車廠變水城！浸壞轉軌器 列車冇法改道","createTime":"2018-08-31T13:47:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T14:07:53.000Z","uid":23707,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6ac8c59501ccc0f3954be3771cbf3226177be8c0","tid":801301,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:47:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180831&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58631073\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180831%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58631073&d=wlg5qpysbMwI8blMwSHqzQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=dd6a7d1e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20180831%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D58631073&h=aa66da5f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20180831&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=58631073</a><br />\n【高鐵通車】紅雨淹車廠變水城！浸壞轉軌器 列車冇法改道"},{"pid":"e68b3d3305f4909b57dec34f3fed4b41f4757906","tid":801301,"uid":23707,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:47:44.000Z","msg":"日前紅雨襲港，高鐵香港段的石崗車廠被洪水倒灌。立法會議員譚文豪今日再取得一批車廠內部相片，可見部分路軌嚴重水浸。譚引述消息稱，該石崗路段負責轉換路軌的路軌轉轍器，在暴雨中被浸壞，要即時更換，他擔心若高鐵通車後，路軌轉轍器再次因下雨故障，如列車駛向錯誤方向，後果或不堪設想。<br />\n<br />\n譚文豪指，從相片中可見，銀白色正方型的部件即為路軌轉轍器，部件內有電動摩打，可以操控路軌改道，據他所知，該路軌轉轍器在紅雨當日，因去水設計出問題被浸壞，令控制室無法控制列車改道。譚認為當日並非百年一遇的大豪雨，但高鐵設計竟然連紅雨考驗都無法通過，明顯是重大缺失，港鐵仍辯稱事件不影響高鐵通車日期。他促港鐵交待在今次紅雨下，車廠共有多少部件損壞及涉的維修費。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》亦接獲消息人士舉報，指紅雨當日車廠內有多處水浸，包括主大樓消防泵房，水深達一呎以上；車輪檢測器在水浸後完全失靈，暫不能監測車輪狀況；有蓋維修車庫有軌道如「河流」般嚴重水浸；控制中心有電子儀器房嚴重滲水；但車廠內沙包嚴重不足，即使手動抽水泵亦只有數個，根本不足以應付豪雨。從讀者提供的相片可見，一段路軌嚴重水浸，流水湧入路軌中央，另一處疑似機房位置，亦嚴重水浸。《蘋果》向港鐵查詢，但暫未有回覆。"},{"pid":"2c709b61fd9cbedf5ec2ebdd2476d78718e2eb39","tid":801301,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:48:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01f8c3fa189c15b24acd25d12cd1b32f63c346f0","tid":801301,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:49:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaa49c382ca46c0c3e8ba112b6eb31e83b248988","tid":801301,"uid":168366,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:49:46.000Z","msg":"今次政治唔關我事班人真係無錯啦<br />\n因為唔會坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d35365b41c12dbc4daa4ac6d71eac31701c9383e","tid":801301,"uid":34517,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:50:25.000Z","msg":"落雨唔好<del>炒蛋</del>坐高鐵"},{"pid":"932f4c0f720dd7cd6c97f3aa014324c55d1cd744","tid":801301,"uid":10680,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:51:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c8b43e0b288d34d61e435fa8400fed261035df85","tid":801301,"uid":73915,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:52:24.000Z","msg":"蘋果幾時開始用「淹」唔係用「浸」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac833e466394e8f1488587f72afcc3da21c2503a","tid":801301,"uid":38666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:52:30.000Z","msg":"沒事兒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94d99f19ec926cec1a7f6ea5d243077dd9b8e110","tid":801301,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:53:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdcf42eac74ff2fcc08f2a153df5271b2d132f9f","tid":801301,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"932f4c0f720dd7cd6c97f3aa014324c55d1cd744","tid":801301,"uid":10680,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:51:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T13:53:37.000Z","msg":"將來會見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12329013132003b4cb9e64cfcf9d4016afbe71da","tid":801301,"uid":1241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl